{"tid":2461033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政權要求外國拒受BNO","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:55:16.000Z","uid":33869,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a448e7c3e95ba9d6afdd1c4c547cdfecb3474d8e","tid":2461033,"uid":33869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"路透社：港府要求外國拒受BNO 外交官：非作為國際金融中心的一貫做法<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述外交官和一封看到的信函報導，香港政府已告知大約12個外國領事館，停止接受英國公民海外(BNO)護照作為旅行證件。報道指，港府稱應該改用香港特區護照。香港自1月31日起，不再將BNO視為有效的旅行證件。香港政府沒有立即回應路透的置評請求。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名外交官表示，此舉並非香港政府一貫注重、作為國際金融中心的傳統做法。<br />\n<br />\n一名西方的資深外交官看過信件後指，大部分國家都會無視此要求。這只是香港政府的嘗試，港府無權要求外國接受或拒絕任何護照。<br />\n\r<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20210325/s00002/1616657763567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20210325%2Fs00002%2F1616657763567&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=7de5e0e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20210325%2Fs00002%2F1616657763567&h=3580cda9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20210325/s00002/1616657763567</a>"},{"pid":"e144465174aeb330ab5235ca0ca675b3031db35b","tid":2461033,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/52a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F52a.gif&h=e409170d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad9cbf2760ae39c24ee87475328befb177cda6eb","tid":2461033,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾香港市，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0c57beddadc6325d085673370baadbc3852b48","tid":2461033,"uid":8257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"咪咁柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用明朝既劍斬清朝既官？"},{"pid":"01adb69bea4d3be60ad02864dd13a84fcc2019f3","tid":2461033,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"哇，真係好撚唔知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b203199e103a0a596d1ca0edde8c9bf76922c77b","tid":2461033,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n港共到底有幾多柒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌訓醒未呀<br />\n仲以為自己係國際金融中心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由你不停拉人屈人坐監個刻已經名聲一路下跌"},{"pid":"2a6aa12cf31534ad7d6db0e7e4b6a0624b4f8468","tid":2461033,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU2cMSenxEjGTvxDSfGocCusp3TnntihSmmEmnoBgZgwM?filename=HQNDWR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQNDWR8.jpg&h=1dc50161&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNoJT6uxY6crHSLFQp8cz4sN2pDFjVLSvK29kNUC7pTCH?filename=2Fdooxa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Fdooxa.gif&h=f4125063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ece92be07cda36422f6d7bedc1bab58f46913d0","tid":2461033,"uid":217257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"干涉外國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81ad0914940bd96f0edc0644d589a62f2125035","tid":2461033,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"憑乜 屌你老母 以為自己真係一個國家?"},{"pid":"232a9e07d64e30a8e9e5d3f5fb0f069263c11f01","tid":2461033,"uid":1865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03